description:
Plain weave with 3 projecting 1 1/4 tubular plain weave flaps. Warp was alternately wound on 2 different beams. Flaps were formed by releasing tension on one beam while maintaining it on the other. 
Warp: 1 wrapped silver, 3 white 2 ply yarns wound a.c. on one beam, b.d. on the other. 
Weft: white textured plied yarn.
